{"word":"κακόφρων","slug":"κακόφρων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κακόφρων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φρήν'><el>φρήν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>ill-minded, malicious, malignant</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>imprudent, thoughtless, heedless</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}